Interior rehab just completed! Move-in ready! Seller has been here since 1990, raised a family here and is ready to move on. It's your family's turn to make some memories. Beautiful home with high ceilings in most areas, a large open kitchen (wood beam ceilings), 3 good sized bedrooms and 2 full baths. Brand new a/c condenser, furnace, kitchen appliances, and granite kitchen countertop. Water heater is less than 3 years old. Where the property is located on this street gives it a larger lot, with tons of fruit trees (jujube, plum, pomegranate, cherimoya, guava, cherry plum, persimmon, calamansi, and mandarin). There is even space for RV parking. Located in the Ramona neighborhood, this home is located within the original boundaries of the City of Riverside when it was first founded in 1883. It's even located within the SAME city block as the historic Riverside Heritage Home (City Landmark #5) with nearby Cal Baptist University. Come check it out before it's gone!Call or text;; <a href="#" class="show-contact" title="click to show contact info" data-href="/reply/inl/apa/7517495659/__SERVICE_ID__" rel="nofollow">show contact info</a><br>
